{"word":"G4748 - στοιχέω - stoichéō - stoy-kheh'-o - Walk","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στοιχέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">stoichéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">stoy-kheh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Walk</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நட"},{"paragraph":"1. to proceed in a row, go in order"},{"paragraph":"2. to walk"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <b>&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C7;&#x03C9;</b> <b>steicho&#x0304;&#x0304;</b> (to <i>range</i> in regular line); to <i>march</i> in (military) rank (<i>keep step</i>), that is, (figuratively) to <i>conform</i> to virtue and piety: - walk (orderly).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4747/4747\">G4747</a>, <a href=\"#/G4748/4748\">G4748</a>, <a href=\"#/G4960/4960\">G4960</a>"}]}